title: British Prime Minister says 18 countries will expel Russian intelligence officers
text:
British Prime Minister says 18 countries will expel Russian intelligence officers Monday, March 26, 2018 - 00:55 
British Prime Minister says 18 countries will expel Russian intelligence officers, leading to the largest Western expulsion of Russian diplomats since the Cold War. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
